<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Blossom2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Blossom,</orth> vb., to put forth blossoms: <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.353" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 353</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.383" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 383</bibl>. <cit><quote>--ing time,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 1.4.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. I, 4, 41</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>melt their sweets on --ing Caesar,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 4.12.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 12, 23</bibl></cit>.
